{"pin":"BH00545","subcodes":[{"code":"BH00545","anchor":"","first_line":"Verily He is, in this hour, alive in this glorious and resplendent horizon. He doth witness and behold and speaketh, addressing the concourse [3.5s]... ...Every word that proceedeth out of the mouth of God is endowed with such potency as can instill new life into every human frame, if ye be of them that comprehend this truth","first_line_orig":"انه هو حینئذ حی فی هذا الافق العزیز المنیر یشهد و یری و یقول مخاطبا لملا  ","language":"1","word_count":"1360","subjects":"@rejection, opposition and persecution, @mysteries and their discovery; the mystical vision, @detachment; severance; renunciation; patience, @sacrifice of the Manifestation of God redeems the world, @teaching the Cause; call to teach, @holy war [jihad]; violence in the name of God","notes":" \u003ca href=\"http://web.archive.org/web/20070930181707/http://bahai-library.com/resources/leiden.list/leiden.list.html#394\"\u003eLL#394\u003c/a\u003e","translations":[],"writing_refs":[{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"pt","lang_name":"Portuguese"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ro","lang_name":"Romanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sq","lang_name":"Albanian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"sv","lang_name":"Swedish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ta","lang_name":"Tamil"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"tvl","lang_name":"Tuvalu"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"de","lang_name":"German"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"es","lang_name":"Spanish"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"lv","lang_name":"Latvian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"ru","lang_name":"Russian"},{"type":"gleanings","type_name":"Gleanings","language":"zh-Ha